{
  "texts": [
    "To identify the effect of note length on the QA model's performance, we calculate the length of the contexts (i.e., notes) in the three test sets and bin them into four quartiles based on their ascending lengths.",
    "Supplementary Data 1 and the x-axis in Fig. 3a show the length range of these bins, whereas the green bars with the right y-axis show the sample count for each bin.",
    "We find that note length does not have any notable effect on the model's performance scores, demonstrated in Supplementary Data 1 and on the left y-axis of Fig. 3a.",
    "Effect of question length.",
    "We also examine the effect of question length on the performance of the QA model."
  ]
}